/-! ### Eventually -/

/-- `f.Eventually p` or `∀ᶠ x in f, p x` mean that `{x | p x} ∈ f`. E.g., `∀ᶠ x in atTop, p x`
means that `p` holds true for sufficiently large `x`. -/
protected def Eventually (p : α → Prop) (f : Filter α) : Prop :=
  { x | p x } ∈ f
